{"tid":402433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由回收紙皮就可以知道香港有幾無能","createTime":"2017-09-16T12:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T11:29:22.000Z","uid":117310,"like":605,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"2f77718b9d32d961553a848d827556125f3ba974","tid":402433,"uid":117310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"大陸一講唔收香港就即刻收皮<br />\n通街紙皮冇人收<br />\n香港人幾時醒覺<br />\n有d野真係要靠自己<br />\n否則人地講一句就即刻收皮<br />\n政府咁多錢搞好d產業啦<br />\n人地新加坡都可以自給自足<br />\n香港就係到炒數字<br />\n唉可悲"},{"pid":"b7b3b70d2fd1697d09a0a6b1f41acf1d88b34bfa","tid":402433,"uid":25560,"like":5,"dislike":195,"score":-190,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"由樓主開始收紙皮？"},{"pid":"7040f9fa8be12444cea1d0e9d05ef7912e69de94","tid":402433,"uid":54733,"like":10,"dislike":102,"score":-92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"支持樓主開廠搞紙皮加工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7722edb8dba3d9bf6f61ad95ac8a2adc62f9c13c","tid":402433,"uid":3122,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"可以睇到一D野"},{"pid":"eb72bb2d324dd27c150060cc31c95b6ca73d6992","tid":402433,"uid":117310,"like":165,"dislike":11,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"見到咁多紙皮冇人要<br />\n好心痛<br />\n利申環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港始終要靠人<br />\n可悲af<br />\n注定收皮"},{"pid":"f86d1ef96f8f2fc6dd42188fc626a7f4abe0edce","tid":402433,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:42:58.000Z","msg":"無其他地方回收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1806a8898792c649e91576954001b331047082f2","tid":402433,"uid":102096,"like":22,"dislike":136,"score":-114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52b7c0751df7dbeca00a9f9fb1bd2e0f7771a35b","tid":402433,"uid":41818,"like":