都話d癈中on9，你支持中共佢唔會多謝你，你有利用價值（可被屠宰），絕不留手，唔關你之前咩政見愛唔愛黨既事。香港既存在價值一直都係因為同中共有距離，如果冇保持距離香港只不過係中國幾百個二線城市既其中之一。"},{"pid":"606816077276a505a2996846385a8635a4cedd12","tid":402433,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:21:29.000Z","msg":"香港乜q都太依賴中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5945d1388eddf3fb5c07f6d75cb5723c69259a","tid":402433,"uid":52651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"仲學人搞環保，而家連紙皮都回收唔番到，你收咩垃圾費?"},{"pid":"40e50b8880ade0756c007f417d9d816cc592d6c6","tid":402433,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港乜q都太依賴中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實可以唔駛"},{"pid":"89bd98cb8132f4246665f45e076ff40000d18337","tid":402433,"uid":46644,"like":8,"dislike":29,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5b2ed23486d7a839f15442b82273d7d645b4fa3","tid":402433,"uid":23162,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"咁咪好囉，睇住班廢老成日阿支阿左話大6點好點好，依家一嘢就俾人揸爆個春袋，爽皮吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3b0713e21fd28d9e515ba19eed2304a0621cdc","tid":402433,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7be26a3879b644ebc82367c1d943129b09b3d4c6","tid":402433,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"樓主收開？<br />\n我賣呀"},{"pid":"02c091d27e0fea16333c816cae7bebcb08585592","tid":402433,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明大陸真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n的確係"},{"pid":"c347e301ee29f58977de2d182af2d4b76f13c8f0","tid":402433,"uid":55597,"like":15,"dislike":2,