quote><br />\n我只是一個普通毒j"},{"pid":"0b67ed93a785b54afb88eb73b21bdfb20bfaa418","tid":402433,"uid":117310,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔收咪好囉 <br />\n唔使一街都係阿婆 喺度執紙皮喇</blockquote><br />\n最衰係d 婆婆靠尼d維生<br />\n唉佢地日子又更難了<br />\n社會基層問題幾時受重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9566f4dd4c49546c5849ea1042bd6d2fff44b611","tid":402433,"uid":80294,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔收咪好囉 <br />\n唔使一街都係阿婆 喺度執紙皮喇</blockquote><br />\n最衰係d 婆婆靠尼d維生<br />\n唉佢地日子又更難了<br />\n社會基層問題幾時受重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n綜援 加生果金 點都有 幾千蚊啩<br />\n加埋公屋免租 日日都有 百零蚊洗下<br />\n可能有啲人會話唔夠使<br />\n有啲人會話想儲多啲<br />\n但唔係 一定要執紙皮先 有飯開<br />\n相反 我有時行過公園 細商場 會見到好多 阿伯 阿婆坐曬喺度 發吽哣<br />\n我諗 可能無聊先係 佢哋執紙皮嘅原因"},{"pid":"dadbe295ba7d0d0a11609dd7e1fc0560c2f28b2c","tid":402433,"uid":9284,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔收咪好囉 <br />\n唔使一街都係阿婆 喺度執紙皮喇</blockquote><br />\n最衰係d 婆婆靠尼d維生<br />\n唉佢地日子又更難了<br />\n社會基層問題幾時受重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 