圾桶旁邊，起碼叫集中有人收)<br />\n<br />\n呢d舊區要大大個垃圾桶分布先應付到.....仲話收細垃圾桶口或減桶都弱智</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新發展市區就話有完善配備仲亂扔就無情講<br />\n舊區根本時與俱進唔到<br />\n<br />\n垃圾收費處理又統一性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547e390f63f8ef60f3f4a52f6ad958dca20c6e8e","tid":402433,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:51:05.000Z","msg":"唔收廢紙已經咁 <br />\n到時唔用新垃圾袋掉出街食環係咪真係唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389d7c81acd1d4590d6bb33e8af10ce0d52926c5","tid":402433,"uid":67280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸一講唔收香港就即刻收皮<br />\n通街紙皮冇人收<br />\n香港人幾時醒覺<br />\n有d野真係要靠自己<br />\n否則人地講一句就即刻收皮<br />\n政府咁多錢搞好d產業啦<br />\n人地新加坡都可以自給自足<br />\n香港就係到炒數字<br />\n唉可悲</blockquote><br />\n賣比第二個國家lo，又懶中國，唔好話你班垃圾依懶中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啦，咁叻叻仲唔快啲幫班回收商物識邊個國家可以收紙，仲話自由轉口港，明明咁好機會話比中央聽你唔收我都有方法散，但結果就係上網鳩叫話比人聽自己幾冇能，仲懶香港人唔醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五毛我未呀，你班垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n我都係上網鳩叫，但唔會好似樓主咁撚on9懶香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2805aa9f00e1ea49dfc07a0dcb402d9ee7090e82","tid":402433,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>證明大陸真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"